:"2020-06-04T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZ0osAh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZ0osAh.gif&h=1d885a1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"708322c554b52ff8c961e7c99a00c40ab17d71f1","tid":2050634,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"又引撚晒啲五毛狗入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ac1269dddb327d4f18946ac395a334afac62ff","tid":2050634,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da82f6f2d8344a99ae586c940e99234566e17bd","tid":2050634,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"相關案例\t編輯<br />\n<br />\n2017年11月14日，內蒙古自治區赤峰市寧城縣一名王姓網絡男主播利用快手平台以惡搞形式演唱《義勇軍進行曲》，隨後被網友指出違規，並遭到舉報。2018年10月30日，寧城警方在官方微信公眾號發布消息稱，已對該男子處以行政拘留15日[53]。<br />\n<br />\n2018年10月7日，虎牙主播「莉哥」（本名楊凱莉）在直播過程中，篡改國歌曲譜，以嬉皮笑臉的方式演唱國歌第一句，並將國歌作為自己「網絡音樂會」的「開幕曲」。10月10日，虎牙發布通報，稱其行為違反了《中華人民共和國國歌法》中奏唱國歌時應當舉止莊重的相關規定。對此，虎牙平台決定即日起封禁主播「莉哥」直播間，凍結主播莉哥直播帳號，下架全部相關影像作品，並對其進行整改教育[54]。10月13日，上海靜安警方通報，已依法對楊凱莉處以行政拘留5日[55]。"},{"pid":"1e9049c2adfa4ee5f9168bf1c2b6d550039d8b5e","tid":2050634,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:35:18.000Z","msg":"為配合國歌，不願做奴隸㗎(香港)人民站起來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7212befdcd6784d5d095019da566e8ec73238c","tid":2050634,"uid":273627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afb2f42dc1a654db1447fb6f9715e0561b2d74bd","tid":2050634,"uid":27432,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:59:56.000Z","msg":"肯認輸未?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">未</span><img s